{
"#name"
:
{
"claw"
:
null
,
"cn"
:
"x-cmd AI 消息机器人"
,
"en"
:
"x-cmd AI message bot"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
{
"x claw <subcmd>"
:
null
}
]
,
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"自托管 AI Agent 网关，将 LLM 接入微信、飞书、Telegram 等即时通讯平台。\n监听 IM 消息并触发本地 AI Agent 执行自主任务，支持通过 `x agent request` 调用\nkimi-cli, claude, codex, gemini-cli, opencode 等多种 AI 引擎，\n每个会话拥有独立 workspace 与持久化上下文记忆。\n"
,
"en"
:
"A self-hosted AI Agent gateway that connects LLMs to WeChat, Feishu, Telegram and other IM platforms.\nListens for IM messages and triggers local AI Agents to execute autonomous tasks,\nsupporting multiple AI engines via `x agent request` (kimi-cli, claude, codex, gemini-cli, opencode),\nwith independent workspaces and persistent context memory per session.\n"
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"使用 'x claw run' 启动消息监听服务（默认微信）。\n支持的 IM 平台: weixin, telegram, feishu, qywx。\nAI Agent 引擎可通过 x-cmd agent 配置切换（如 kimi-cli, claude, codex, gemini-cli, opencode）。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Use 'x claw run' to start the message listener (default: WeChat).\nSupported IM platforms: weixin, telegram, feishu, qywx.\nAI Agent engine can be switched via x-cmd agent config (e.g. kimi-cli, claude, codex, gemini-cli, opencode).\n"
}
]
,
"#subcmd:Service"
:
[
"run"
]
,
"#subcmd:inner"
:
[
"weixin"
,
"telegram"
,
"feishu"
,
"agentrequest"
]
,
"run"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"启动 AI Agent 消息监听与处理服务，连接指定 IM 平台并实时触发 AI Agent 自主处理与回复。"
,
"en"
:
"Start the AI Agent message listener and processing service, connecting to the specified IM platform and triggering AI Agent autonomous processing and replying in real-time."
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
{
"x claw run [im]"
:
null
}
]
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"即时通讯平台名称（默认 weixin）"
,
"en"
:
"IM platform name (default: weixin)"
}
,
"#cand"
:
[
"weixin"
,
"telegram"
,
"feishu"
,
"qywx"
]
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"该命令在前台运行，保持终端打开以持续监听消息。如需后台运行，请配合 screen/tmux 或使用 service 命令。\n启动前请确保已配置对应的 IM 平台服务（如 `x weixin bot service ensure`）。\n新消息到达时自动分派到独立 worker 处理。\nAI Agent 回复引擎由 `x agent request` 决定，支持 kimi-cli, claude, codex, gemini-cli, opencode 等。\n内置心跳机制与 x cron 集成，支持定时唤醒和 proactive 任务执行。\n每个 chat 拥有独立 workspace 与持久化上下文记忆，支持多会话并发。\n"
,
"en"
:
"This command runs in the foreground; keep the terminal open to continue listening. Use screen/tmux or the service command for background execution.\nEnsure the corresponding IM platform service is configured before starting (e.g. `x weixin bot service ensure`).\nDispatches incoming messages to independent workers for processing.\nThe AI Agent reply engine is determined by `x agent request`, supporting kimi-cli, claude, codex, gemini-cli, opencode, etc.\nBuilt-in heartbeat mechanism with x cron integration supports scheduled wake-ups and proactive task execution.\nEach chat has an independent workspace with persistent context memory, supporting multi-session concurrency.\n"
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x claw run"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 启动微信消息监听服务"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Start the WeChat message listener"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x claw run telegram"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 启动 Telegram 消息监听服务"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Start the Telegram message listener"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x claw run feishu"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 启动飞书消息监听服务"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Start the Feishu message listener"
}
]
}
,
"agentrequest"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"向 AI Agent 发送消息请求（内部命令）。"
,
"en"
:
"Send a message request to the AI Agent (internal command)."
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
{
"x claw agentrequest <im> <chatid> <msg>"
:
null
}
]
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"即时通讯平台名称（如 weixin, telegram, feishu）"
,
"en"
:
"IM platform name (e.g., weixin, telegram, feishu)"
}
}
,
"#2"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"聊天会话 ID"
,
"en"
:
"Chat session ID"
}
}
,
"#3"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"要发送的消息内容"
,
"en"
:
"Message content to send"
}
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"此命令为内部接口，通常由 IM 服务自动调用。"
,
"en"
:
"This is an internal interface, usually invoked automatically by the IM service."
}
]
}
,
"weixin"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"微信消息查询工具"
,
"en"
:
"WeChat message query tools"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
{
"x claw weixin <subcmd>"
:
null
}
]
,
"#subcmd:Query"
:
[
"get-msg"
,
"unread-count"
,
"recent-msg"
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x claw weixin get-msg 100:200"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 获取第 100 到 200 行的消息"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Get messages from line 100 to 200"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x claw weixin get-msg 50"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 从第 50 行开始获取到文件末尾"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Get messages from line 50 to end of file"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x claw weixin unread-count"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 查看微信未读消息数"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Show WeChat unread message count"
}
]
,
"get-msg"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"按行号范围获取消息"
,
"en"
:
"Get messages by line range"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
"<start>[:<end>]"
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"行号范围（如 100:200）或起始行号"
,
"en"
:
"Line range (e.g., 100:200) or start line"
}
}
,
"#2"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"结束行号（可选，与起始行号一起使用）"
,
"en"
:
"End line number (optional, used with start line)"
}
}
}
,
"unread-count"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"显示未读消息数量"
,
"en"
:
"Show unread message count"
}
}
,
"recent-msg"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"显示最新所有未读的消息"
,
"en"
:
"Show all recent unread messages"
}
}
}
,
